//How to How to use the app: Press anywhere on the camera screen to start the search. The app will analyze the image and search the database using the word(s) with the biggest size. Please place the text you are about to scan as close to the camera as possible for the best result. There is also the option of searching using manual input. Click on the search bar to type. The app will store the last 10 items found during searches. Click to view them again. In the results view, clicking on one of the active substances will result in a Google search for that perticular substance.
